## Phase 2 — Update Test Cases

### Status update — Start of Phase 2

Per `workflows/checkpoint-protocol.md` §2 (write-before-work rule):

1. **Worklog**: rewrite last entry → `status = "Running (Phase 2: Update Test Cases)"`. Append input file names to `input` (excluding `process-logging/` and `progress-logging/`).
2. Do NOT modify deliverable test case files yet.
3. Do NOT convert to `.xlsx` in this phase.

